    Attribute, Date, Entity, Event, Time

    public class Element
extends org.apache.uima.jcas.cas.TOP
    A basic semantic unit that refers to something in the real world, including Entities, Events, Attributes, Dates. Element inherits from uima.cas.TOP to combine textual mentions of these real-world objects. Updated by JCasGen Thu Jun 20 11:44:40 CEST 2019 XML source: /home/siabar/eclipse-workspace/ctakes/ctakes-type-system/src/main/resources/org/apache/ctakes/typesystem/types/TypeSystem.xml
